    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Bloodrager - Bloodline</strong><br/><br/><p>Your body is suffused with raw plant life. When you bloodrage, your plantlike characteristics bolster your durability and grant you some control over vegetation.</p><p><b>Bonus Feats: </b>Bolstered Resilience, Diehard, Endurance, Great Fortitude, Power Attack, Raging Vitality, Toughness.</p><p><b>Bonus Spells: </b>entangle (7th), greensight (10th), burst of nettles (13th), command plants (16th)</p><p><b>Bloodline Powers: </b>While bloodraging, you gain plantlike abilities and immunities as you become overgrown with jagged branches, rugged bark, and thick vines.</p>",
